-----------------
INFO:
-----------------
This is the first map ever created by Ambiance Mapping. We are a new group of mappers and hope to bring many exciting maps to the CSS public community. Join the Steam Community "Ambiance Mapping" we have over 150 supporters. Criticism is appreciated. Enjoy.

-----------------
INSTALLATION:
-----------------

Extract the content into..

".../steam/steamapps/username/counter-strike source/cstrike"

If you previously installed any Ambiance versions, overwrite everything when asked.
